info.description:
whoami
======
::

    easypwd
    easy password generate libary


version
========
::

    0.3.7

License
=========
::

    GPL
    GNU General Public License

install
=========
::

    unzip easypwd-0.3.7.zip to c:\easypwd-0.3.7\
    c:\easypwd-0.3.7>setup.py install
    OR
    pip install easypwd

author
=======
::

    L34Rn

email
======
::

    security@xatu.edu.cn

orginazation
=============
::

    xatusec

url
=====
::

    http://security.xatu.edu.cn/

support os
============
::

    Windows

support python version
========================
::

    2.6
    2.7

functions
===========
::

    md5(password_length)
    weak(password_length)
    normal(password_length)
    strong(password_length)
    very_strong(password_length)

lib
====
::

    >>> easypwd.md5(20)
    'cc19224f51ebdaebbc97'
    >>> easypwd.weak(20)
    '37363766808224449490'
    >>> easypwd.strong(20)
    'wSYEWP5N13xKzN9G6Un6'
    >>> easypwd.very_strong(20)
    '^6!z3**$tH7J^oR&f&!1
    >>> for x in xrange(10):
            easypwd.very_strong(20)
    '$U%$*X$87#M*^k2bU^!%'
    '#~#5*z5ld#1sg^&&W#9O'
    'K@@^*!*#nY!7Wp*!Ay&1'
    '7cgD@*8%1^c!%K#j*@6H'
    'd@*~Q@y@*FMw$$@u$*~$'
    '1#^4z@8&*!&3~~*^~KW^'
    '%qG&!48~g0$6m^#%6ZBz'
    '#d7!xh1E#W8$*~^#%69G'
    '9l~%^f~VWg*&!5*6*#~5'
    'n$9nnD@#%%3X%~149$Iy'
